      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I already tried talking to people. It doesn't change the reality. The truth is, that version of me is just gone. Like, there's no coming back from that. It's like I'm just a ghost haunting my own life, and honestly, it feels more like an inconvenience to everyone else than a person. It just feels exhausting to keep pretending there's something actually \"alive\" here.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
