      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not a storm that passes. it's just... nothingness. there's no one to hold my hand because there's nothing left to hold onto. like i said, the person they actually need is gone. they're just living with a memory of someone that doesn't exist anymore. it would be so much simpler if the reality actually matched the void.",
